{"tid":1286534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"777只剩下警察","createTime":"2019-07-05T01:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T02:42:32.000Z","uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45389f4cc92dcbb2559fce6ab2e16e0e06ffc8bd","tid":1286534,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:42:03.000Z","msg":"777政府已經得罪<br />\n1. 記者界<br />\n2. 法律界<br />\n3. 醫護界<br />\n4. 教育界<br />\n5. 商界<br />\n6. 媽媽聯盟<br />\n7. 海外傳媒<br />\n8. 宗教界<br />\n9. 藥劑界<br />\n10. 社工界<br />\n11. 勞工界<br />\n12. 其他專業界別<br />\n<br />\n割蓆系列亦無窮盡，連行政會議自己都開唔到<br />\n<br />\n呢個政府已經眾伴親離，對香港內部已經無能力管治，對外國際社會亦一面倒支持香港人。所以林鄭6.16之後第一時間，會見自己的下屬香港警察，因為係制度下，佢只剩番呢一個工具。<br />\n<br />\n用警棍，白色恐怖可以解決呢場運動？絕對唔可能，反而刺激更多和理非同情示威者，加入佢地的行列。777同中共政權已經一錯再錯，不斷誤判，結果必然失敗收場。"},{"pid":"fcac28015e89b45a4922cce8061ab15ab3f305ae","tid":1286534,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21f210dac237c40801e1045cb1bc41115a840e65","tid":1286534,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}